Package: confusR
Type: Package
Title: Functions to help make sense of confusion matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Lovell
Maintainer: David Lovell <David.Lovell@qut.edu.au>
Description: Tools to analyse confusion matrices from binary or multinomial classifiers by expressing them in terms of 
    classifier-dependent likelihood ratios and test-data-dependent prior odds
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
